Class JLExtensionInfo

java.lang.Object
polyglot.frontend.AbstractExtensionInfo
polyglot.frontend.ParserlessJLExtensionInfo
polyglot.frontend.JLExtensionInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
ExtensionInfo
Direct Known Subclasses:
ExtensionInfo, JL5ExtensionInfo, JLOutputExtensionInfo
public class JLExtensionInfo
extends ParserlessJLExtensionInfo
This is the default ExtensionInfo for the Java language. Compilation passes and visitors:
  1. parse
  2. build-types (TypeBuilder)
    3. BARRIER
  3. disambiguate (AmbiguityRemover)
  4. type checking (TypeChecker)
  5. reachable checking (ReachChecker)
  6. exception checking (ExceptionChecker)
  7. exit checking (ExitChecker)
  8. initialization checking (InitChecker)
  9. circular constructor call checking (ConstructorCallChecker)
    PRE_OUTPUT MARKER
  10. serialization (ClassSerializer), optional
  11. translation (Translator)
